data.description: Welcome to Bayport, a gated community of Huntington Harbour.  This end unit offers a spectacular view of the Marina and nearby coastal ocean landscapes. This is truly a waterfront gem spanning 2,118 sqft of luxury living. It's equipped with an en-suite bedroom on the first floor which could be used as an office or study while the second floor offers a master bedroom with private balcony and view of the harbor plus a third large bedroom.  Also, this home comes with three and a half bathrooms. Including sizable closets to accommodate all of your accessories. Plus, the kitchen offers plenty of amenities and a formal dining room with a view.  As you step inside, you will be greeted with a spacious and open floor plan.  There are also 2 fireplaces to keep you cozy and comfortable.  Down on the lower level, there is a 2-car garage with direct access into the home.  Additionally, there is a super large basement that can be converted into storage space for your personal belongings. Located adjacent to Peters Landing Marina and a short walk across the street to the beach. Plus, the conveniences include nearby restaurants and shopping. The Bayport community offers security gates, clubhouse room, BBQ area pool, spa, and sports court.  The Bayport community is currently under renovation to improve balcony railings and replacement of stucco wall with smooth design.  This unit currently has a leased slip that can accommodate up to 50ft vessels.
